140
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,000
Shen Cheng!

141
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,040
Careful.

142
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,639
Stop!

143
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:35,160
Careful.

144
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,160
Shen Cheng!

145
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,639
