153
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:25,639
Yes.

154
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,080
I used to live here.

155
00:08:27,919 --> 00:08:29,120
We went to investigate.

156
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,159
Some old neighbors

157
00:08:30,159 --> 00:08:31,600
