159
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,960
A year before?

160
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,360
That's him, right?

161
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,679
That's my father when he was young.

162
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,360
His name is Tang Yixun.

163
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,720
In 1991,

164
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,639
