172
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,799
and died in prison.

173
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:08,399
I think he received

174
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,799
Yu Zhiyong's dying wish

175
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,399
to go to your hometown

176
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:13,519
and care for you and your grandma.

177
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:20,960
Just...

178
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,759
